              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Car Rental for usage within Langkawi."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Many types of car to be choose from."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Air-conditioned car."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Convenient Pick-Up:Airport/Jetty Pickup: Enjoy a seamless start to your adventure with pickup directly from Langkawi International Airport or the jetty. Your air-conditioned car will be ready and waiting, ensuring a comfortable journey from the moment you arrive.Full-Day Road Trip:Explore Langkawi: Embark on a full-day road trip across the island, visiting its most iconic and popular attractions.Top Destinations: Visit must-see spots such as Tanjung Rhu Beach, known for its pristine sands and stunning views, and other notable landmarks.Multi-Day Car Rental:Extended Exploration: Opt for a multi-day car rental if you wish to take your time exploring Langkawi at your own pace, discovering hidden gems and less-visited areas.Flexible Itinerary: Enjoy the flexibility to create your own itinerary, allowing for spontaneous stops and extended visits to your favorite spots.Langkawi Underwater World:Marine Wonderland: Discover one of Malaysia’s largest aquariums, Langkawi Underwater World, where you can marvel at a diverse array of marine life.Educational Experience: Learn about different marine species and ecosystems, making it an educational and entertaining stop for all ages."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
